<tr>
<th class="" style="padding:0.1em;;background:lightskyblue;;">Areas of study</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="" style="padding:0 0.1em 0.4em; font-size:105%;;"><a href="Accent_(dialect)" title="Accent (dialect)" class="mw-redirect">Accent</a>&#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span> <a href="Dialect" title="Dialect">Dialect</a><br />
