<th class="" style="padding:0.1em;;background:lightskyblue;;">Key concepts</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="" style="padding:0 0.1em 0.4em; font-size:105%;;"><a href="Code-switching" title="Code-switching">Code-switching</a>&#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span> <a href="Diglossia" title="Diglossia">Diglossia</a><br />
