<th class="" style="padding:0.1em;;background:lightskyblue;;">People</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="" style="padding:0 0.1em 0.4em; font-size:105%;;"><a href="Category_Sociolinguists" title="Category:Sociolinguists">Sociolinguists</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="" style="padding:0.3em 0.4em 0.3em;font-weight:bold;background:none;"><b><a href="Category_Sociolinguistics" title="Category:Sociolinguistics">Category:Sociolinguistics</a><br />
<a href="Portal_Linguistics" title="Portal:Linguistics">Portal:Linguistics</a></b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:right;font-size:115%;">
<div class="noprint plainlinks hlist navbar mini" style="">
